I applied for a sapphire preferred and was approved, same day I applied for this one and got denied. Reason given was “to many requests for credit, or open accounts with us” I have total 3 inquiries, with the last one being a year old, and I have 2 chase cards including the sapphire” thank you HMBC for everything!
Third AMEX business card, sixth overall. Also have their savings account and business checking account. No hard pull, but did request bank account information.
Thank you HMPC, non stop free advice, and the best credit card search engine by far!
Got declined cause I past the 5/24 had to call in a few time’s reconsideration that some of the cards are only authorized users and that I don’t manage the payments. Thanks #HMBC!
They took a soft inquiry and then told me whether I was approved and then allowed me to decide if I wanted to accept and they then pulled a credit report.
